    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Àrengard-Invasion</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is a small online party game developed by myself in 2 weeks (LionDev) to learn multiplayer game development in Unreal Engine and how to publish a game on Steam so don't expect too much. <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select one out of four classes and prepare your castle for the Goblins siege in this &quot;classic&quot; mode. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Features:</i> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classes (Archer, Soldier, Mage, Defender) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighting (PVE / CO-OP) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control siegeengines </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different enemy classes (Bomber, Soldier, Siegeengines) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn gold</p></li></ul>",
